thread.title: Mari Licking
thread.title_full: Cambridge Proofreading reviewed by Mari Licking

author: Mari Licking
title: Mari Licking
text: Having a important paper to submit for your Master's program is always a nail-biter but even more so when the university writing lab is closed for Spring Break. Needing an academic level edit I turned to Cambridge Proofreading and I am tremendously pleased with their work. I thought the rates were very reasonable and the turn around was perfect. I also had a sense that my paper what just as important to them as it is to me. That put me at ease! I excited to see my final grade!!
